# pCloud sync-conflict artifacts (the repo lives inside a pCloud dir
# on the developer's machine; pCloud writes these files when two
# devices touch the same file). Never belong in source control.
# Match the literal "conflicted" substring — `*[conflicted]*` would be
# treated as a character class and match almost every filename.
*conflicted*
